<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>rby ạ̉nt ạlʿwn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- rby ạ̉nt ạlʿwn ạ̉nt nṣrty ạ̉rtjy kẖlạṣk rby ạnt fy ḥmạk nṣrty ạ̉rtjy kẖlạṣk
 rby ạ̉msk bymynk ydy rby kẖlṣ nfsy ạ̉nt mnjdy
 (kẖlṣ nfsy ḥbyby sydy)2(ạ̉rtjy kẖlạṣk)2
 2- rby jạʿt nfsy wạlqlb kẖwy̱ ạ̉rtjy kẖlạṣk
 rby ạ̉nt qwt nfsy wạldwạ ạ̉rtjy kẖlạṣk
 rby fạ̉qrb mny wạ̉ṭfỷ lwʿty rby wạqrb mny ʿz mhjty
 (rby frḥ nfsy ạ̉nt frḥty)2 (ạ̉rtjy kẖlạṣk)2
 3- mn swạk sydy nfsy yryḥ ạ̉rtjy kẖlạṣk
 rby ạ̉nt fyk qlby ystryḥ ạ̉rtjy kẖlạṣk
 rby hạt ạlʿwn ly mn qdsk rby wạsnd mhjty fy ḥḍnk
 (ạ̉ʿṭny ạbtsạmh mn tẖgẖrk)2 (ạ̉rtjy kẖlạṣk)2</lyrics>
<author>zkryạ ʿwḍ ạllh, d/ ạ̹ylyạ zkryạ</author>
